ype":"HowToStep","position":"2","name":"<p>Bootstrapping.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>Using your own money and resources to fund your courier service can be a good approach. There are always risks involved with starting a new business, and if you can remove debt from the equation, you automatically minimize those risks.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.notzarla.com/guides/how-to-start-a-courier-service#how-to-start-a-courier-service-section5-step2","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-bootstrapping-288x288-20200819.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"}},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"3","name":"<p>Get help from friends and family.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>Before seeking external funding for your courier service, ask those in your immediate circle. Make sure you have a business plan ready, that you are able to present all the facts and projections to your friends and family, and that there is a clear understanding of whether they stand to gain anything from investing in your business.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.notzarla.com/guides/how-to-start-a-courier-service#how-to-start-a-courier-service-section5-step3","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-get-help-from-friends-and-family-288x288-20200819.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"},"itemListElement":[{"@type":"HowToTip","text":"<p>Friends and family may be more willing to help you than a formal institution as they already trust you and are familiar with your character.<\/p>\n"},{"@type":"HowToTip","text":"<p>You may be able to negotiate lower interest rates or repayment terms than a  bank would offer you.<\/p>\n"},{"@type":"HowToTip","text":"<p>Have a formal written agreement drawn up so that all parties are clear on repayments, profits, etc.<\/p>\n"}]},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"4","name":"<p>Start a crowdfunding campaign.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>Setting up a crowdfunding page might be a viable option 