w who your potential clients are, you have a better chance of reaching them.<\/strong> <\/p>\n<p>There are several ways to market your courier service. Some methods will not cost you a dime, while others can set you back hundreds of dollars. Carefully consider who you need to reach and the channels available to you.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.notzarla.com/guides/how-to-start-a-courier-service#how-to-start-a-courier-service-section10-step1","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-know-who-your-target-audience-is-before-you-start-your-marketing-campaign-288x288-20200819.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"}},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"2","name":"<p>Use the internet.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>It is absolutely free to register your business on LinkedIn, Facebook, Instagram, and Twitter.\nUsing these platforms will help <strong>increase brand visibility<\/strong> and also allow you to have <strong>meaningful interactions with your clients<\/strong> and the broader public. There are also free email marketing services you could use to inform clients about upcoming promotions.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.notzarla.com/guides/how-to-start-a-courier-service#how-to-start-a-courier-service-section10-step2","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-use-the-internet-288x288-20200817.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2","height":"288","width":"288"}},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":"3","name":"<p>Network with key players.<\/p>\n","text":"<p>Approach businesses that are likely to require courier services so you can secure long-term clients. Another great way of expanding your client base is to attend events where you can meet potential clients.<\/p>\n","url":"https://www.notzarla.com/guides/how-to-start-a-courier-service#how-to-start-a-courier-service-section10-step3","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-network-with-key-players-288x288-20200817.jpe